- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with developing a pipeline system to parse raw tweets into UD. 
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is a less likely category as the paper does not explicitly mention the use of neural networks or evolutionary algorithms, but it is possible that these techniques were used in the parser development. 
- cs.CY (Computers and Society) is the least likely category as the paper does not focus on the societal implications of parsing tweets into UD.
